## Play music

```
mpv *.mp4 --no-video --loop
```


`--loop` to loop the playlist, `--loop-file` to loop playlist entries.


## Shuffle


```
--shuffle
```


## Play all in the directory


```
mpv ./* --shuffle --loop --no-video
```
